<h2>What is Sumatra PDF?</h2>

<!--
<img align="right" src="http://kjkpub.s3.amazonaws.com/blog/sumatra/SumatraSplash.png" hspace="4"/>
-->

<p>Sumatra PDF is a slim, free, open-source PDF reader for Windows. Portable out of the box.</p>
<h2>Why another PDF reader?</h2>
<p>Sumatra has a minimalistic design. Simplicity has a higher priority than a lot of features.</p>
<p>It's small and starts up very fast.</p>
<p>It's designed for portable use: only one file so you can run it from external USB drive. Doesn't write to registry.</p>

